# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:43
translate spanish hwb_s16c_9548ba85:

    # "Solid ground feels foreign after the rocketing motorhome. This must be what it feels like to return from a voyage at sea."
    "El suelo firme se siente extraño después de la casa rodante a toda velocidad. Esto debe ser lo que se siente al regresar de un viaje en el mar."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:45
translate spanish hwb_s16c_8f0543bc:

    # "Marina, the landlubber, doesn’t seem to be having any trouble now that we’re not barrelling along the highway."
    "Marina, la terrestre, no parece tener ningún problema ahora que no vamos a toda velocidad por la carretera."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:49
translate spanish hwb_s16c_b2235a5d:

    # "The spring in her step has returned, and I worry that she’s going to bang the metal detector against the ground as she half-walks, half-skips."
    "El brinco en su paso ha vuelto, y me preocupa que vaya a golpear el detector de metales contra el suelo mientras camina y brinca a medias."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:53
translate spanish hwb_s16c_a0b23df9:

    # "Some of the other people watch us go, but no one follows or says anything. They probably assume we’re just next in the line of failures."
    "Algunas de las otras personas nos miran irse, pero nadie nos sigue ni dice nada. Probablemente asumen que somos solo las siguientes en la fila de fracasos."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:55
translate spanish hwb_s16c_fe2caf30:

    # "A line which must be pretty long, given how much trash and misplaced earth there is around here."
    "Una fila que debe ser bastante larga, dado toda la basura y tierra desplazada que hay por aquí."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:57
translate spanish hwb_s16c_4e254ad6:

    # "Pangs of guilt remind me yet again of the broken brick at Canyon de Chelly, and I make my umpteenth resolution to be more careful."
    "Punzadas de culpa me recuerdan una vez más el ladrillo roto en Canyon de Chelly, y hago mi enésima promesa de ser más cuidadosa."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:59
translate spanish hwb_s16c_9974b702:

    # "Just ahead, Marina’s come to a stop. Head tilted back, I can tell she’s admiring Balanced Rock."
    "Justo adelante, Marina se ha detenido. Con la cabeza inclinada hacia atrás, puedo decir que está admirando Balanced Rock."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:61
translate spanish hwb_s16c_9866a635:

    # "It’s certainly an impressive view."
    "Ciertamente es una vista impresionante."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:63
translate spanish hwb_s16c_22c7bc81:

    # "Someday, I’d like to take her back to all these places we’ve gone, but without the pressure of the treasure hunt rushing us. Just taking in the sights."
    "Algún día, me gustaría llevarla de vuelta a todos estos lugares que hemos visitado, pero sin la presión de la búsqueda del tesoro apurándonos. Solo disfrutando del paisaje."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:65
translate spanish hwb_s16c_f9b46766:

    # "I slow my steps a little, so I can keep watching her from behind."
    "Disminuyo un poco el paso para poder seguir mirándola desde atrás."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:67
translate spanish hwb_s16c_eda87039:

    # "Maybe sensing me, she spins around and waves."
    "Quizás sintiéndome, se da la vuelta y saluda."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:71
translate spanish hwb_s16c_b18ad639:

    # Marina "Hurry up!"
    Marina "Давай быстрей!"

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:73
translate spanish hwb_s16c_4551ed47:

    # "Yelling, even though I’m close enough to hear her normal volume level."
    "Gritando, aunque estoy lo suficientemente cerca para oírla a volumen normal."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:75
translate spanish hwb_s16c_f744ff77:

    # "I pick up the pace once more."
    "Acelero el paso de nuevo."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:81
translate spanish hwb_s16c_02d8c37c:

    # Marina "So, where was Chip?"
    Marina "Ну что, где эта “маленькая копия”?"

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:83
translate spanish hwb_s16c_185f43cb:

    # Amber "Over there, to the right."
    Amber "Вон там, справа от нас."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:85
translate spanish hwb_s16c_a035c55d:

    # "There’s a large stone wall besides Balanced Rock itself, with a short slope between them."
    "Hay un gran muro de piedra junto a la Roca Equilibrada, con una pendiente corta entre ellos."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:87
translate spanish hwb_s16c_588ed48e:

    # Amber "It was right at the edge of that little hill."
    Amber "Она находилась рядом с этим холмом."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:91
translate spanish hwb_s16c_04bdde56:

    # Marina "So where that pile of rocks is now?"
    Marina "А, там где теперь лежит вот эта груда камней?"

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:95
translate spanish hwb_s16c_55b26752:

    # Amber "Yep, that’s the spot."
    Amber "Ага, прямо тут."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:97
translate spanish hwb_s16c_66f7ccd4:

    # "You can’t tell that there used to be anything there. But I’ve seen pictures in the atlases Gramps kept around, or in the history books he liked to read."
    "No se nota que solía haber algo allí. Pero he visto fotos en los atlas que el Abuelo guardaba, o en los libros de historia que le gustaba leer."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:99
translate spanish hwb_s16c_c65ade6d:

    # "Compared to Balanced Rock, Chip Off the Old Block looked tiny. But it was actually a decent size."
    "Comparado con la Roca Equilibrada, el Pedazo del Bloque Original parecía diminuto. Pero en realidad era de un tamaño decente."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:101
translate spanish hwb_s16c_2fb3cb09:

    # "There’s a pile of stones at the base that are probably Chip’s remains. They’re indistinguishable from the rest of the red rocks, though."
    "Hay un montón de piedras en la base que probablemente son los restos del Pedazo. Aunque son indistinguibles del resto de las rocas rojas."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:103
translate spanish hwb_s16c_6d571994:

    # "Some are as big as my head, or even bigger."
    "Algunas son tan grandes como mi cabeza, o incluso más."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:105
translate spanish hwb_s16c_bba3b894:

    # "It’s hard to tell if anyone else has picked through here. But since there aren’t any shovel marks or holes, I’m guessing not."
    "Es difícil saber si alguien más ha revisado esto. Pero como no hay marcas de pala ni agujeros, supongo que no."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:107
translate spanish hwb_s16c_67ae873a:

    # Marina "Where do we start?"
    Marina "С чего начнем?"

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:111
translate spanish hwb_s16c_a3506f66:

    # "I think for a moment."
    "Pienso por un momento."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:115
translate spanish hwb_s16c_f5414b3a:

    # Amber "First, let’s get the easy stuff out of the way. You go check that side with the metal detector, and I’ll check this one."
    Amber "Давай начнем с простого. Ты проверь ту сторону металлоискателем, а я проверю вот эту."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:117
translate spanish hwb_s16c_bc1f9251:

    # "We sweep over the ground between the hill where Chip once stood and the massive stone wall beside it."
    "Rastrillamos el suelo entre la colina donde una vez estuvo el Pedazo y el enorme muro de piedra a su lado."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:119
translate spanish hwb_s16c_9850f53c:

    # "Nothing."
    "Nada."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:123
translate spanish hwb_s16c_61e867d3:

    # Amber "Okay, that’s pretty much what I expected."
    Amber "Окей, это было вполне ожидаемо."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:125
translate spanish hwb_s16c_fb2fbeb2:

    # "I lean my metal detector against the wall and go back to the pile of rocks."
    "Apoyo mi detector de metales contra el muro y vuelvo al montón de rocas."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:129
translate spanish hwb_s16c_8271dc96:

    # Amber "Just check over the places that I uncover, okay?"
    Amber "Проверяй те места, которые я буду расчищать."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:133
translate spanish hwb_s16c_293e738d:

    # "Marina nods, holding her detector at the ready. She reminds of a surgeon, about to perform an operation."
    "Marina asiente, sosteniendo su detector listo. Me recuerda a un cirujano a punto de realizar una operación."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:135
translate spanish hwb_s16c_df1fba37:

    # "I roll aside some of the rocks with my feet, but most are so big that I have to stoop down and use my hands."
    "Aparto algunas rocas con los pies, pero la mayoría son tan grandes que tengo que agacharme y usar las manos."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:137
translate spanish hwb_s16c_f1ec6b4a:

    # "There are more of them than I thought, and I’m soon sweaty and sore."
    "Hay más de las que pensaba, y pronto estoy sudada y adolorida."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:141
translate spanish hwb_s16c_6bcc7c86:

    # Marina "Do you want any help?"
    Marina "Помощь нужна?"

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:145
translate spanish hwb_s16c_b9b4b6a4:

    # Amber "Nah."
    Amber "Не."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:147
translate spanish hwb_s16c_946f7ebc:

    # "I’m panting."
    "Estoy jadeando."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:149
translate spanish hwb_s16c_3ab93856:

    # Amber "Just keep scanning."
    Amber "Просто продолжай сканировать."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:153
translate spanish hwb_s16c_3e32ae27:

    # "She does so, dutifully retracing my steps. Still, nothing."
    "Ella lo hace, siguiendo obedientemente mis pasos. Aun así, nada."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:155
translate spanish hwb_s16c_56c553e4:

    # "After a couple minutes, I stand up and take a swig from a water bottle. I’m glad I remembered to bring them this time."
    "Después de un par de minutos, me levanto y tomo un trago de una botella de agua. Me alegra haber recordado traerlas esta vez."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:157
translate spanish hwb_s16c_097c0cd1:

    # "Marina sets down her metal detector to do the same."
    "Marina deja su detector de metales para hacer lo mismo."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:161
translate spanish hwb_s16c_d2f015c4:

    # Marina "D’you think Tess and them are okay?"
    Marina "Как думаешь Тесс и ребята там в порядке?"

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:163
translate spanish hwb_s16c_7f4a5131:

    # Amber "Why wouldn’t they be?"
    Amber "С чего бы им не быть в порядке?"

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:167
translate spanish hwb_s16c_699d547c:

    # Marina "Don’t you think Mariah’s gonna flip out when she realizes she took the wrong turn?"
    Marina "Ты не думаешь, что Мария сойдет с ума, когда поймет, что повернула не туда?"

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:169
translate spanish hwb_s16c_09602d8a:

    # Amber "Probably. That’s her fault, though."
    Amber "Возможно. Но она сама виновата."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:171
translate spanish hwb_s16c_67c196d6:

    # Marina "Not like you would’ve let her go down this side of the road!"
    Marina "Не похоже было, что ты давала ей шанс свернуть в ту же сторону, что и мы!"

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:175
translate spanish hwb_s16c_f0c768e4:

    # Amber "Hey, I did what I had to do."
    Amber "Хэй, я делала то, что было необходимо."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:179
translate spanish hwb_s16c_a2be7783:

    # Marina "Uh huh. But you’re never doing that again, okay?"
    Marina "Ага. Но давай ты не будешь больше так делать, окей?"

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:183
translate spanish hwb_s16c_ae22d1ed:

    # Amber "If we get the next treasure, too, I won’t have to."
    Amber "Если мы найдем и следующую часть  клада, то мне и не придется."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:185
translate spanish hwb_s16c_88a88ed1:

    # Marina "When we get it, you mean."
    Marina "Ты хотела сказать “когда мы его найдем”, так ведь?"

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:189
translate spanish hwb_s16c_b0d72ae3:

    # Amber "Right. When."
    Amber "Да. “Когда”."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:191
translate spanish hwb_s16c_2b7113ea:

    # "Only one more to go after this. One more frantic search and then…"
    "Solo queda una más después de esta. Una búsqueda frenética más y luego..."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:193
translate spanish hwb_s16c_e41d332a:

    # "I drain my water bottle and crumple it up before shoving it into my pocket."
    "Vacío mi botella de agua y la aplasto antes de meterla en mi bolsillo."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:199
translate spanish hwb_s16c_675ad9fb:

    # Amber "Break’s over. Back to work."
    Amber "Перерыв закончился. Пора возвращаться к работе."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:201
translate spanish hwb_s16c_770cb27d:

    # "I pop my back and resume moving rocks out of the way. I’ve been working from the outer edge of the rock pile inward, since they’re more concentrated in the center."
    "Estiro la espalda y reanudo el movimiento de las rocas. He estado trabajando desde el borde exterior del montón hacia adentro, ya que están más concentradas en el centro."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:203
translate spanish hwb_s16c_a1fd1f79:

    # "Like a shadow, Marina continues to stick to me, going where I go."
    "Como una sombra, Marina sigue pegada a mí, yendo a donde yo voy."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:205
translate spanish hwb_s16c_a2afb5c3:

    # "Nearly ten minutes of uninterrupted shuffling pass. By now, I’m expecting Mariah to have caught up, or to get here soon."
    "Casi diez minutos de arrastres ininterrumpidos pasan. Para ahora, espero que Mariah nos haya alcanzado, o que llegue pronto."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:207
translate spanish hwb_s16c_b874e1b9:

    # "But she never arrives. Maybe she just gave up."
    "Pero nunca llega. Quizá simplemente se rindió."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:209
translate spanish hwb_s16c_2bb3b001:

    # "Although, knowing Mariah, that’s just wishful thinking."
    "Aunque, conociendo a Mariah, eso es solo un pensamiento iluso."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:211
translate spanish hwb_s16c_c162a6fd:

    # "I’ve just finished moving a torso-sized rock when it happens."
    "Acabo de terminar de mover una roca del tamaño de un torso cuando ocurre."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:213
translate spanish hwb_s16c_0dbfb1a7:

    # "The metal detector begins to chirp, bright and earnest."
    "El detector de metales empieza a chirriar, brillante y entusiasta."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:217
translate spanish hwb_s16c_62263c1f:

    # "Marina and I exchange a look, and I nod."
    "Marina y yo intercambiamos una mirada, y yo asiento."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:221
translate spanish hwb_s16c_ddade84f:

    # Marina "I’ll get the shovel!"
    Marina "Я возьму лопату!"

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:227
translate spanish hwb_s16c_8be427a5:

    # "It’s leaning up against the wall by the second metal detector. Marina grabs it, starts back towards me, then doubles back to set her detector aside as well."
    "Está apoyado contra la pared junto al segundo detector de metales. Marina lo agarra, vuelve hacia mí, luego retrocede para dejar su detector también a un lado."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:231
translate spanish hwb_s16c_61151638:

    # "I move to take the shovel from her, but she holds it away, shaking her head."
    "Me muevo para tomarle la pala, pero ella la aparta, negando con la cabeza."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:233
translate spanish hwb_s16c_0f2c90ab:

    # Marina "Nuh uh. You moved all the rocks."
    Marina "Не-а, ты разгребала камни."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:237
translate spanish hwb_s16c_285bb069:

    # Amber "Yeah, but I-"
    Amber "Да, но я..."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:239
translate spanish hwb_s16c_0ad5f912:

    # "She frowns at me, and I can tell this is an argument I won’t win."
    "Me frunce el ceño, y sé que esta es una discusión que no voy a ganar."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:243
translate spanish hwb_s16c_42c60e01:

    # Amber "Okay, okay. Be careful though. Don’t throw out your shoulder."
    Amber "Окей, окей. Будь осторожнее. Не вывихни плечо."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:247
translate spanish hwb_s16c_ace280b3:

    # Marina "I know what I’m doing!"
    Marina "Я знаю, как копать!"

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:249
translate spanish hwb_s16c_3e595873:

    # "And she stabs at the ground like she’s wielding a salad fork."
    "Y clava la pala en el suelo como si estuviera manejando un tenedor de ensalada."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:251
translate spanish hwb_s16c_057a0093:

    # "It bounces off with a jolt."
    "Rebota con un tirón."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:255
translate spanish hwb_s16c_5e1893d7:

    # Amber "You need to go at it with more of an angle. Like you’re trying to slide it into the ground."
    Amber "Тебе нужно взять угол побольше. Чтобы лопата как-бы скользила в землю."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:257
translate spanish hwb_s16c_ad191030:

    # "I move behind her and adjust her arms a little. Her shoulders are damp with sweat, though I’m drenched with it."
    "Me coloco detrás de ella y le ajusto un poco los brazos. Sus hombros están húmedos de sudor, aunque yo estoy empapada."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:259
translate spanish hwb_s16c_02d6d4d6:

    # "She tenses up when I first touch her, but relaxes almost immediately."
    "Se tensa cuando la toco por primera vez, pero se relaja casi de inmediato."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:261
translate spanish hwb_s16c_4fa291a0:

    # "It’s enough to make me self-conscious though, and I take a quick step back."
    "Sin embargo, es suficiente para ponerme cohibida, y doy un paso rápido hacia atrás."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:265
translate spanish hwb_s16c_927286b4:

    # Amber "Sorry."
    Amber "Прости."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:267
translate spanish hwb_s16c_c12a03db:

    # "I’m mumbling."
    "Estoy murmurando."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:271
translate spanish hwb_s16c_64d78863:

    # Marina "Oh, no, you’re fine! You just surprised me."
    Marina "О, нет, все в порядке! Ты просто немного удивила меня."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:273
translate spanish hwb_s16c_49d38e51:

    # "Her voice is higher than usual."
    "Su voz es más aguda de lo normal."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:277
translate spanish hwb_s16c_f6b2e2b0:

    # Amber "It’s okay, you should have it now."
    Amber "Ну, сейчас должно получаться лучше."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:279
translate spanish hwb_s16c_82b37214:

    # "Nodding, Marina jabs at the ground again. She scoops out a little bit of dirt and dumps it aside."
    "Asintiendo, Marina vuelve a clavar la pala en el suelo. Saca un poco de tierra y la tira a un lado."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:283
translate spanish hwb_s16c_4c6cf06f:

    # "Watching her dig is painful. Either the ground is hard, or she’s not strong enough to make fast progress."
    "Verla cavar es doloroso. O el suelo está duro, o ella no es lo suficientemente fuerte para avanzar rápido."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:287
translate spanish hwb_s16c_56bccac5:

    # "Whatever the reason, it’s slow going. But she refuses my repeated offer to take going, so with my hands on my hips, I watch as the hole very slowly gets deeper."
    "Sea cual sea la razón, va lento. Pero rechaza mi oferta repetida de tomar el relevo, así que, con las manos en las caderas, observo cómo el hoyo se hace más profundo muy lentamente."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:291
translate spanish hwb_s16c_97475a0a:

    # "She’s reached a depth of maybe a foot or so when the shovel thumps against something that isn’t dirt."
    "Ha alcanzado una profundidad de quizás un pie cuando la pala golpea algo que no es tierra."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:297
translate spanish hwb_s16c_98fb3504:

    # "Our eyes instantly meet."
    "Nuestras miradas se encuentran al instante."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:302
translate spanish hwb_s16c_cadf5a3c:

    # "I stoop down and brush a little bit of dirt away from the shovel blade. Sure enough, I can feel rough wood just under my fingertips."
    "Me agacho y aparto un poco de tierra de la hoja de la pala. Efectivamente, siento madera áspera justo bajo mis dedos."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:306
translate spanish hwb_s16c_35fad0d1:

    # Marina "Is it…?"
    Marina "Это...?"

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:310
translate spanish hwb_s16c_e6f1bc78:

    # Amber "Yeah, it is."
    Amber "Да."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:314
translate spanish hwb_s16c_7dad89f7:

    # "Now she forces the shovel towards me."
    "Ahora ella me empuja la pala hacia mí."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:318
translate spanish hwb_s16c_88a0f2a9:

    # Marina "I don’t wanna mess it up."
    Marina "Не хочу все тут испортить."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:320
translate spanish hwb_s16c_08e06d10:

    # Amber "Okay, look out."
    Amber "Ладно, отойди немного."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:325
translate spanish hwb_s16c_f05febe8:

    # "She steps back a couple feet, but leans forward to watch."
    "Retrocede un par de pies, pero se inclina hacia adelante para mirar."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:327
translate spanish hwb_s16c_9f1411c5:

    # "I scrape at the dirt around the spot that we hit, trying to find where the edges are."
    "Raspo la tierra alrededor del lugar donde golpeamos, tratando de encontrar dónde están los bordes."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:329
translate spanish hwb_s16c_5e32c978:

    # "Once I reveal one corner, I start to dig off thin slices of dirt next to it."
    "Una vez que descubro una esquina, empiezo a cavar finas capas de tierra a su lado."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:331
translate spanish hwb_s16c_b81efac9:

    # "Soon the outline of the whole box is visible."
    "Pronto el contorno de toda la caja es visible."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:336
translate spanish hwb_s16c_a9a5b056:

    # "I hear Marina suck in a sharp breath. My heart is pounding with the same cautious excitement I felt at Shiprock."
    "Escucho a Marina jadear bruscamente. Mi corazón late con la misma emoción cautelosa que sentí en Shiprock."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:338
translate spanish hwb_s16c_681c4431:

    # "It hardly feels real and yet…"
    "Casi no se siente real y sin embargo…"

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:340
translate spanish hwb_s16c_0f5d075d:

    # "Well, there’s only a ten percent chance that I’m dead and it isn’t."
    "Bueno, solo hay un diez por ciento de probabilidad de que esté muerta y no lo sea."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:345
translate spanish hwb_s16c_5cbc1b9c:

    # "I lift the box out of the ground with the blade of the shovel, and Marina plucks it off."
    "Levanto la caja del suelo con la hoja de la pala, y Marina la arranca."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:347
translate spanish hwb_s16c_1c3183e1:

    # "It makes a familiar rattling sound as she moves it."
    "Hace un sonido familiar de traqueteo mientras la mueve."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:353
translate spanish hwb_s16c_828df7c1:

    # Marina "Amber…"
    Marina "Эмбер!"

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:355
translate spanish hwb_s16c_9445ee03:

    # "But I hold up a dirty finger to my lips."
    "Pero levanto un dedo sucio hacia mis labios."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:361
translate spanish hwb_s16c_8b6f8551:

    # Amber "Not yet."
    Amber "Рано."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:365
translate spanish hwb_s16c_c5daac79:

    # "Looking back towards the parking lot, I can’t tell if anyone has seen us."
    "Mirando hacia el estacionamiento, no puedo decir si alguien nos ha visto."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:367
translate spanish hwb_s16c_ccfbad2b:

    # "Seen us dig, and find the treasure."
    "Nos ha visto cavar y encontrar el tesoro."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:371
translate spanish hwb_s16c_c0c7a861:

    # Amber "Don’t say anything until we get back to the car."
    Amber "Ничего не говори, пока не доберемся до машины."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:373
translate spanish hwb_s16c_50fc2baa:

    # "She’s a quivering leaf of excitement, but she manages to keep her mouth mostly shut for now."
    "Es una hoja temblorosa de emoción, pero logra mantener la boca mayormente cerrada por ahora."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:375
translate spanish hwb_s16c_085c6deb:

    # "But not before hissing out an excited \"{cps=6}Amberrrrrr.\"{/cps}"
    "Pero no sin antes sisear un emocionado \"{cps=6}Amberrrrrr.\"{/cps}"

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:379
translate spanish hwb_s16c_4f89ff4c:

    # "I just smile, hoping that I look calm."
    "Solo sonrío, esperando parecer tranquila."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:381
translate spanish hwb_s16c_93ce4a8c:

    # "Marina cradles the box in the crook of her arm like an infant, doing her best to keep it hidden from onlookers as we head back to the motorhome."
    "Marina acuna la caja en el hueco de su brazo como a un bebé, haciendo todo lo posible por mantenerla oculta de los mirones mientras regresamos a la casa rodante."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:383
translate spanish hwb_s16c_33064d03:

    # "She carries the shovel in her free hand, while I have both metal detectors."
    "Lleva la pala en su mano libre, mientras yo tengo ambos detectores de metales."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:385
translate spanish hwb_s16c_6d5b1ea4:

    # "I don’t even notice the soreness in my arms."
    "Ni siquiera noto el dolor en mis brazos."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:133
translate spanish hwb_s16c_d9554a0d:

    # "Marina nods, holding her detector at the ready. She reminds me of a surgeon, about to perform an operation."
    "Marina asiente, sosteniendo su detector listo. Me recuerda a una cirujana, a punto de realizar una operación."

# game/script/hwb_s16c.rpy:287
translate spanish hwb_s16c_9e887434:

    # "Whatever the reason, it’s slow going. But she refuses my repeated offer to take over, so with my hands on my hips, I watch as the hole very slowly gets deeper."
    "Sea cual sea la razón, avanza lento. Pero rechaza mi oferta repetida de tomar el relevo, así que con las manos en las caderas, observo cómo el agujero se vuelve muy lentamente más profundo."

